317	The Gift	Region	0101000000576C2934FAEC4040010000E0A25A3340	The Gift, consisting of Brandon's Gift and the New Gift, is the area in the north stretching fifty leagues south from the Wall, land given to the Night's Watch in perpetuity to support and aid the Watch. It is under the protection of both the Watch and Winterfell. The eastern lands of the Gift consist of large rolling plans that reach the Shivering Sea, while the western regions, which end at the Bay of Ice, are increasingly forested and mountainous.	https://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php/Gift
