320	The Riverlands	Region	010100000070AFE06317312440010000C054392B40	The riverlands is a central region of the Seven Kingdoms of Westeros, consisting of the rich, fertile, and populous areas around the three forks of the Trident and the northern Blackwater Rush. At the time of Aegon's Conquest the riverlands and the Iron Islands were ruled by House Hoare, the Kings of the Isles and the Rivers, although native river kings ruled centuries earlier.	https://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php/Riverlands
321	The Kingswood	Region	010100000025BF6F5371AD064001000080B8E13240	The kingswood is a large forest that lies across the Blackwater Rush from King's Landing. It is in the southern crownlands and the northern stormlands and is traversed by the kingsroad.	https://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php/Kingswood
322	The Wolfswood	Region	0101000000B33A9E89BC033D4001000080C3B22840	The wolfswood is a large forest in the north named for the great many wolves one can hear howling in the night.	https://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php/Wolfswood
323	The Westerlands	Region	010100000038CE6AC7945B1840010000806D262940	The westerlands is a region in the west of the continent of Westeros. Before Aegon's Conquest, it was known as the Kingdom of the Rock. People from the westerlands are known as westermen. The customary surname of bastards of noble origin born in the westerlands is Hill.	https://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php/Westerlands
324	The Sunset Sea	Region	01010000001F95204ECB4FE9BF01000000003C0E40	The Sunset Sea or sunset sea is a sea to the west of Westeros. It borders the Reach, the westerlands, the Iron Islands, the riverlands, the north, and the lands beyond the Wall.	https://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php/Sunset_Sea
325	The Iron Islands	Region	01010000006209B9FB18C12840000000006ECF1C40	The Iron Islands is one of the constituent regions of the Seven Kingdoms. Until Aegon's Conquest it was ruled by the Kings of the Iron Islands and then briefly the Kings of the Isles and the Rivers.	https://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php/Iron_Islands
326	The Stormlands	Region	010100000083B723EED18CD3BF0100008084133540	The stormlands are one of the constituent regions of the Seven Kingdoms on the continent of Westeros. The Kingdom of the Storm was a sovereign nation until Aegon's Conquest, in which the last Storm King was slain. The region is so-named for the savage and frequent autumn storms that batter the coast after beginning in the Summer Sea.	https://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php/Stormlands
